TELESCOPE
space pv: go to netrw 
space pf: find files
space ps: grep
Ctrl+p  : git find files

UNDOTREE
space u : undo tree

FUGITIVE
space gs: git

HARPOON
space a : add file
Ctrl+e  : menu
Ctrl+t  : file 1
Ctrl+h  : file 2
Ctrl+n  : file 3

LSP ZERO
Ctrl+p  : prev
Ctrl+n  : next
Ctrl+y  : confirm
Ctrl+Spc: complete
	['<C-p>'] = cmp.mapping.select_prev_item(cmp_select),
	['<C-n>'] = cmp.mapping.select_next_item(cmp_select),
	['<C-y>'] = cmp.mapping.confirm({ select = true }),
